org.transitime.core.travelTimes

Class TravelTimeInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.transitime.core.travelTimes.TravelTimeInfo
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TravelTimeInfoWithHowSet

    public class TravelTimeInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    For holding the GPS based travel times for each trip/stop path. Contains the trip info so can determine things such as the trip pattern and the trip start time so that can find best match for when GPS data is not available for a particular trip.
    Author:
    SkiBu Smith
